Package com.flag4j.operations.dense.real_complex

Class RealComplexDenseElemDiv

java.lang.Object
com.flag4j.operations.dense.real_complex.RealComplexDenseElemDiv
public class RealComplexDenseElemDiv extends Object
This class contains low-level implementations of element-wise tensor division for a real dense and complex dense tensor.

    • useConcurrent

      private static boolean useConcurrent​(int numEntries)
      Chooses if a concurrent algorithm for element-wise multiplication should be used based on the shape of the two tensors.
      Parameters:
      numEntries - Total entries in the tensors to multiply.
      Returns:
